task.summary:
Add new style.css file for the website design
Added a new css stylesheet to create the new design of the website. This file contains all the styles used for different webpages and helps in maintaining a consistent theme throughout our website. The style.css includes styles for various elements such as body, headers, links, and multiple custom classes.
